00:04:38.920 --> 00:04:46.100
I saw them, and I started to lean towards being a doctor

00:04:46.100 --> 00:04:51.240
During my summer break in High School,
I told my father about this

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:53.340
He was surprised

00:04:53.980 --> 00:05:00.000
And said that he thought I wanted to be
a singer and a gymnast

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:05.040
I thought that I had to put my hobbies aside
And got serious about studying

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:09.180
But my parents said that maybe I could sing, dance,
and be a doctor at the same time

00:05:09.180 --> 00:05:12.460
My parents weren’t as strict about studying all the time

00:05:12.460 --> 00:05:18.160
So I was able to continue my hobbies and pursue medicine

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.460
