or there are eyelashes that are upside down turned inside

00:06:07.320 --> 00:06:11.300
There are many troubles that come with eyelids

00:06:11.300 --> 00:06:16.260
In Kanazawa University, there was no specialization in this

00:06:16.260 --> 00:06:18.860
